# Everything in .goat-flow/ is gitignored EXCEPT config.yaml, tasks/, and logs/sessions/
# config.yaml is committed — the whole team shares the same paths
# handoff-template.md is committed — shared template for session handoffs
# logs/sessions/ directory is committed (contents gitignored) so router table path resolves
*
!.gitignore
!config.yaml
!tasks/
!logs/
!logs/sessions/
!logs/sessions/.gitkeep
